snippet.title: Wedding Families can Withdraw upto Rs 2.5 Lakhs amid Demonetisation

localized.description:
Note ban: Modi government eases wedding woes. Families can withdraw upto Rs 2.5 lakhs. Peoples are facing challenges to exchange and deposit old notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
